answers.answer: I would go because a sudden onset of migraines (whether you've had them before or not) can be a sign of preeclampsia

question: I have suffered from migraines most of pregnancy up until about 29 weeks they just disappeared. I'm now on day 2 with a migraine, and taking the v recommended dose of the meds my ob had prescribed, I can barely function... I just  started having stomach contractions, my back hurts non stop now too...
title: 36weeks 6days, should I go to l&d?!
